{"title":"HTML5","date":"2021-05-13T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 14, 2021","L":"05/14/2021","MM-DD":"05-14"},"link":"2021/05/14/HTML&CSS/HTML5进阶","categories":["HTML&CSS进阶"],"updated":"2021-05-18T10:09:34.105Z","content":"<h1 id=\"html5进阶\">HTML5进阶<a title=\"#html5进阶\" href=\"#html5进阶\"></a></h1>\n<p>结构化元素：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">section</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">header</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">footer</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">nav</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">article</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">aside</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">main</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>无明确语义：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>在没有合适于一元素的情况下，<code>div</code>仍然是给内容分组的一个不错选择</li>\n<li>纯粹出于添加样式的目的，e.g. 实现居中布局</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>：段落标签  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">time</span>&gt;</span>：标记时间和日期  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">q</span>&gt;</span>：标记引用  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">em</span>&gt;</span>：标记需要强调的内容  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">strong</span>&gt;</span>：标记需要重点强调的内容  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">hr</span>&gt;</span>：水平线标签</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重设样式：Eric Meyer的<a href=\"https://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/css/reset/\" target=\"_blank\">CSS React</a> 和 Nicholas Gallagher的<a href=\"https://jerryzou.com/posts/aboutNormalizeCss/\" target=\"_blank\">Normalize.css</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"css选择符\">CSS选择符<a title=\"#css选择符\" href=\"#css选择符\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>基本选择符：类型和后代（空格）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>精确选择目标元素：ID选择符（#）和类选择符（.）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>高级选择符：</p>\n<p>子选择符（&gt;）：只选择一个元素的直接后代</p>\n<p>相邻同辈选择符（+）：位于某个元素后面并与该元素拥有共同父元素的元素</p>\n<p>一般同辈选择符（~）：<code>h2~p&#123;&#125;</code>可以选择<code>h2</code>后的所有段落</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>通用选择符（*）：可以和上面的三个高级选择符结合，选择某个特定的嵌套层次<code>.product-section &gt; * &#123;&#125;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>属性选择符</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>伪元素（::）：<code>.chapter::before</code>，<code>::first-letter</code>，<code>::first-line</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>伪类（:）：<code>a:link</code>，<code>a:visited</code>，<code>a:hover</code>，<code>a:focus</code>，<code>a:active</code></p>\n<p>结构化伪类（<code>:nth-child()</code>等等）：仅列出该例，其它自己查</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 从第<span class=\"number\">1</span>行开始，把奇数或偶数的背景变成黄色</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">tr</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:nth-child</span>(odd/even)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: yellow;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 把第<span class=\"number\">3</span>行变黄色</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">tr</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:nth-child</span>(<span class=\"number\">3</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: yellow;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 把<span class=\"number\">4</span>，<span class=\"number\">7</span>，<span class=\"number\">10</span>，...变黄色</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">tr</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:nth-child</span>(<span class=\"number\">3</span>n+<span class=\"number\">4</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: yellow;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>表单伪类：详见<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\" target=\"_blank\">网址</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>关于盒模型</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">box-sizing</span>:content-box / border-box</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: block / inline / inline-block</span><br><span class=\"line\">block: 块级，垂直方向，边距由上下外边距决定</span><br><span class=\"line\">inline: 行内，水平方向，水平方向padding和margin决定，垂直高度不受这些影响，即给行内盒子设置明确高宽无用</span><br><span class=\"line\">水平盒子→行盒子：通过line-height来决定高度</span><br><span class=\"line\">inline-block: 被设置元素会像一个行内盒子一样水平排列，但盒子内部仍然像块级元素一样</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>外边距折叠仅发生在块级盒子的垂直方向。行内盒子、浮动盒子或绝对定位盒子外边距不会折叠。</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>关于定位</strong>（定位与浮动）</p>\n<p>绝对定位几乎没人用</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">position</span>: relative / absolute / fixed / static</span><br><span class=\"line\">left: / right: / top: / bottom: </span><br><span class=\"line\">z-index:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>浮动：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">float</span>: left / right / none / inherit;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">clear</span>: both / left / right / none; 指定盒子那一侧不应该紧挨盒子</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>:after</code>模拟额外清除元素</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>关于字体</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">font-family:</span><br><span class=\"line\">font-size: 可以使用Modular Scale计算器查看很多预设的比例关系</span><br><span class=\"line\">ling-height: <span class=\"number\">1.2</span>-<span class=\"number\">1.5</span>之间</span><br><span class=\"line\">vertical-align:</span><br><span class=\"line\">font-weight: <span class=\"number\">100</span>-<span class=\"number\">900</span>, normal:<span class=\"number\">400</span>, bold:<span class=\"number\">700</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">font-style: italic </span><br><span class=\"line\">word-spacing:</span><br><span class=\"line\">letter-spacing:</span><br><span class=\"line\">text-indent: 段首缩进</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">text-align</span>: left / right / center / justify / start / end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>关于背景</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">简写属性：</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: color position size repeat origin clip attachment image</span><br><span class=\"line\">全部属性：</span><br><span class=\"line\">background-color: </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">background-position: <span class=\"number\">50%</span> <span class=\"number\">50%</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">最简单的情况下可以只给两个值，相对左侧偏移量和相对顶部偏移量。使用em或px是图片左上角，使用百分比不太一样</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">background-size: <span class=\"number\">100%</span> auto / contain / cover;</span><br><span class=\"line\">使用百分比和<span class=\"attribute\">auto</span>关键字设置背景大小，可以使背景宽度始终填满元素；</span><br><span class=\"line\">使用contain使浏览器尽可能保持图片最大化，同时不改变图片的宽高比，浏览器自动决定哪一边使用<span class=\"attribute\">auto</span>值</span><br><span class=\"line\">使用cover来使图片缩放以保证覆盖元素的每一个像素，同时不会变量，这种方式图片会被裁剪</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">background-repeat</span>: repear-x / repear-y / no-repeat</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">background-origin: border-box / padding-box / content-box</span><br><span class=\"line\">相对内容框来定位背景图像</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">background-clip: border-box / padding-box / content-box</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">background-attachment: fixed / scroll / local;</span><br><span class=\"line\">背景图像是否固定</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">background-image</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">url</span>(<span class=\"string\">图片地址</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">opacity</span>:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">calc()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">background-position</span>: right <span class=\"number\">1em</span> top <span class=\"number\">50%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">等价</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">background-position</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">calc</span>(<span class=\"number\">100%</span>-<span class=\"number\">1em</span>) <span class=\"number\">50%</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>关于边框</strong></p>\n<p>边框宽度会影响盒子尺寸</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">简写：<span class=\"attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid <span class=\"number\">#000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">boredr-(<span class=\"attribute\">top</span>)-<span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">border-</span>(left)-color:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">border-</span>(right)-style: solid / dashed / dotted / double（双线）/ groove / inset / none;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">0.5em</span> <span class=\"number\">2em</span> <span class=\"number\">0.5em</span> <span class=\"number\">2em</span>; 左上角开始、逆时针</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"每日一题：LC231 2的幂 & LC342 4的幂数","link":"2021/05/31/刷题日记/每日一题：LC231 2的幂 & LC342 4的幂"},"next":{"title":"每日一题：LC1011 在D天内送达包裹的能力","link":"2021/04/26/刷题日记/每日一题：LC1011 在D天内送达包裹的能力"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/05/14/HTML&CSS/HTML5进阶/","toc":[{"id":"html5进阶","title":"HTML5进阶","index":"1","children":[{"id":"css选择符","title":"CSS选择符","index":"1.1"}]}]}